Florence Kahn (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Florence_Kahn_(actress) 0 Florence Kahn (Lady Beerbohm) (born March 3, 1878 in Memphis, Tennessee – died January 13, 1951 in Rapallo, Italy) was a Jewish American actress and the first wife of caricaturist and parodist Sir Max Beerbohm.
